</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-24_ pf-text-1"><strong>Regulated qualifications</strong> - Ofqual oversees GCSEs, A-levels, and vocational qualifications, impacting millions of students annually.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-26_ pf-text-1"><strong>Standards maintenance </strong>- Ofqual conducts regular reviews and updates to qualification frameworks, ensuring they remain relevant and rigorous.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-28_ pf-text-1"><strong>Stakeholder engagement</strong> - Ofqual works closely with awarding bodies, educational institutions, employers, and government departments to uphold standards.
